gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 129, Clippers 107
gameRecap.excerpt: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander totaled his league leading fortieth 30-point game with 31 points, eight assists, and four rebounds as the Thunder defeated the Clippers, 129-107. Lu Dort (19 points), Jalen Williams (18 points, 6 assists), and Chet Holmgren (17 points, 10 rebounds, three blocks) added 54 points in the win. Kawhi Leonard (20 points, three rebounds) and James Harden (17 points, six rebounds) led Los Angeles in the loss.
